Some devices only show a directory with a tree structure similar to a Windows Finder and some recognize both (iriver, Samsung, Sony, Cowon, smartphones with operating system).
The player tries to serve, the mobile knows more
For the choice of a specific equipment you are interested in the resistance of the accumulator, the capacity of the memory, the quality and type of sound output and, of course, the comfort of its handling.
If you listen, above all, to music as a background and are going to listen to it every day for just a while, like on the tram, then it is enough with any mobile that you play.
That's what virtually any mobile really gets.
It should not even be interested in the format in which the mobile or player plays the music.
The MP3 plays it all and almost all the music that comes to you will be in this format.
It is among the most widespread and with the exception of it the absolute majority of the devices play music in WMA format.
The least include the AAC format (format used by Apple and its iPod).
The best mobiles also make it possible, for example, to buy music online.
It is enough through the mobile internet to visit the competent pages of the operator (or any other service provider) and buy a song or album.
This service could by itself be a weighty argument to acquire a mobile for music.
Unfortunately, the offer of operators is miserable and most are limited only to the fleeting success themes of the radios.
The prices are also not the lowest.
However, in general, it is assumed that precisely this way of selling music (either by GSM, internet or wireless internet) in the future will dominate the music industry.
Most people always carry a mobile phone on top of it.
Whenever you want to hear something, you’ll find the phone in your pocket, while the MP3 player will be forgotten at home.
However, it still depends on whether you always carry with you headphones or, at least, handsfree ones.
If not, you can use an integrated player that has virtually every mobile even if it is at least one MP3 player.
Probably the biggest advantage for many of the mobile with music will be its price.
