Again, the advantage of the players is nothing more than their easy service.
The simplest players – by no means necessarily the cheapest (see our selection) – are really managed by anyone.
The minimum functions, its handling similar to the previous current cassettes or also to the tocadiscs is evident.
It does not pose a threat in the sense that by mistake we connect to the internet with the mobile and, consequently, gigantic counts for data loss.
What device to choose
Even the cheapest phones (e.g., the Vodafone 527) usually have a slot to change the memory card (M2, micro SD, etc.).
Even with the purchase of a suitable card will reach the two thousand crowns.
However, be careful.
